'''馬克·奧斯汀'''（Mark William Austin，{{bd|1958年|11月1日}}）是一位[[英國|英國]][[記者|記者]]和電視節目主持人。他是[[ITV新聞|ITV新聞]]的主要主持人之一，現在是[[ITV晚間新聞|ITV晚間新聞]]的兩位主持人之一。他也是[[獨立電視台|獨立電視台]]紀錄片[[真實犯罪|真實犯罪]]的節目主持人。在進入ITV之前，馬克曾經在[[BBC|BBC]]工作過。他最早是一名體育記者。2007年開始，他是[[ITV十點新聞|ITV十點新聞]]的主持人之一<ref>{{cite news |first=Stephen |last=Brook |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/jan/02/itv.tvnews |title=News at Ten date confirmed |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2 January 2008 |accessdate=18 July 2014 |archive-date=2008-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080908030723/http://www.guardian.co.uk/media/2008/jan/02/itv.tvnews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2014年和2015年，他贏得了RTS年度主持人獎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.itv.com/news/2014-02-20/itv-news-wins-four-coveted-royal-television-society-awards/ |title=ITV News wins four coveted Royal Television Society awards |work=ITV News |date= |accessdate=18 July 2014 |archive-date=2017-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170514173339/http://www.itv.com/news/2014-02-20/itv-news-wins-four-coveted-royal-television-society-awards/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他已經結婚並且有三個孩子<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.surreylife.co.uk/people/celebrity-interviews/news_at_ten_s_mark_austin_on_prince_william_and_kate_the_big_stories_and_life_in_the_surrey_hills_1_1957195 |title=News at Ten's Mark Austin on Prince William and Kate, the big stories and life in the Surrey Hills |work=Surrey Life |date=22 February 2013 |accessdate=18 July 2014 |archive-date=2016-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412181157/http://www.surreylife.co.uk/people/celebrity-interviews/news_at_ten_s_mark_austin_on_prince_william_and_kate_the_big_stories_and_life_in_the_surrey_hills_1_1957195 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
